{100}{}{Ghoul}
{200}{}{You see a weird mutant thing with splotchy skin and a ghastly smile.}
{210}{}{You see a ghoul. Its skin looks like it's ready to slough off the creature. It also looks like it's readily accepted by the other townsfolk.}
{1000}{}{Преддиалоговые установки}
{1010}{}{Тупой}
{1020}{}{Не знаком}
{1030}{}{Знаком}
{1040}{}{получил квест на рога изобилия}
{2000}{}{You're not supposed to be here!}
{2010}{}{Da yagga! Eep oop op!}
{2020}{}{Dunno.}
{3000}{}{You're not supposed to be here!}
{3010}{}{Who are you?}
{3020}{}{What is this place?}
{3030}{}{I want some uranium.}
{3040}{}{Nothing.@@Forget it. Bye.}
{4000}{}{What do you want?}
{4010}{}{Da yagga! Eep oop op!}
{4020}{}{Dunno.}
{5000}{}{What do you want?}
{5010}{}{Who are you?}
{5020}{}{What is this place?}
{5030}{}{I want some uranium.}
{5040}{}{Nothing.@@Forget it. Bye.}
{5050}{}{I'm looking for work. Any Ideas what I could do around here?}
{6000}{}{Look @sex@|son||sis|, I'm sorry that you've got no mind. But you can't be here. Run along now.@@You can't be here. It's dangerous. Run along now.}
{6010}{}{[-done-]}
{7000}{}{I'm the supervisor of this refinery. What do you want?}
{7010}{}{What is this place?}
{7020}{}{I want some uranium.}
{7030}{}{Nothing.}
{8000}{}{This is the refinery of Broken Hills. This is where we purify the ore dug from the mine. What do you want}
{8010}{}{I want some uranium.}
{8020}{}{Nothing.}
{9000}{}{Fine. You don't have any business here. Please leave so we can get our jobs done.}
{9010}{}{Bye.}
{10000}{}{Well... OK, the city needs money.}
{10010}{}{Let's see what you've got.}
{10020}{}{Enough trade for today.}
{11000}{}{You look like a serious man. Can you do us a favor? Not for free, of course.}
{11010}{}{I'm tired of doing favors. I don't want to.}
{11020}{}{Spit it out.}
{12000}{}{As you can see, we have a uranium refinery. Here we refine uranium. All clear so far?}
{12010}{}{Yeah, yeah, get to the point.}
{13000}{}{Well, there are rumors that hubologists, these fucktards, these sons of bitches, these…}
{13010}{}{[Get through an avalanche of swearing]}
{14000}{}{…suckers. Wait, where were we?}
{14010}{}{Hubologists are bad.}
{15000}{}{Huh? No, wait. So, they found a way to simplify the ore refining process. And simpler means cheaper, get it? We need this technology. If you can get it, our gratitude will have no limits… err… within reasonable limits.}
{15010}{}{I can get anything out of anyone.}
{15020}{}{I don't mess with hubologists. Sort it out yourselves.}
{16000}{}{What about our agreement?}
{16010}{}{I'm on it… [Leave]}
{16020}{}{Have fun [Give him the disk]}
{16030}{}{I found out everything. They have a neat engineering solution, listen...}
{17000}{}{Well done. Now to my part of the deal. Make a choice: $10000 in cash or a 25% discount on all uranium you buy. And a little something from me personally in any case.}
{17010}{}{Discount. [Leave]}
{17020}{}{Cash. [Leave]}

